    {
      "chinese": "賽德克族有德鹿谷群、德固達雅群、都達群三種語群，因此簡稱「3S3T」。賽德克族德鹿谷群、德固達雅群、都達群的先祖們都相傳過：「起源說」從樹中亮白的石頭。因此，賽德克族德鹿谷群、德固達雅群、都達群三種語群都深信我們是一家人。",
      "ab": "Seejiq, Seediq, Sediq niqan Truku, Tgdaya, Toda tru klgan kari, kiya ni asi slxani tmhangan “3S3T” da. Seejiq Truku, Seediq Tgdaya, Sediq Toda ksun ga ida smnru saw “pnaah Pusu Qhuni/Rmdax Tasil” msa kana ka rdrudan alang. Kiya ni snhiyi balay kingal dara ka Seejiq Truku, Seediq Tgdaya, Sediq Toda.",
